<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prohibit-vt">prohibit <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /prə'hɪbɪt/    美 /prə'hɪbɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-ban-forbid">1.★ <strong>[正式用语] [常用于被动语态] 禁止 (ban / forbid)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Smoking is prohibited.
禁止吸烟。</p><footer>2008 江苏</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>prohibit sb from doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Visitors are prohibited from feeding the animals.
禁止游客投喂动物。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>prohibition /ˌprəʊɪ'bɪʃn/ n   </p></div>